# 🌟 KAIRO – The Smart Life Companion App

KAIRO is an all-in-one AI-powered life assistant that helps people **learn smarter, spend wisely, and stay safer** every day.

---

## 💡 Overview
KAIRO combines **AI automation** and **Composio Tool Router** to create a single app that supports:
- 🎓 **LearnWise AI:** Summarize lectures, notes, and YouTube videos.
- 💰 **SpendWise AI:** Monitor spending, detect fraud, and send alerts.
- 🌸 **WomenAI:** Meal planning, wellness, and emergency SOS with live location.
- 💪 **MenAI:** FixIt guides, affordable self-care, and bachelor meal plans.
- 🌐 **SocioAware AI:** Detect misinformation and promote positive content.

---💬 TalkZone – AI Emotional Support

TalkZone offers users a private, judgment-free zone to express feelings and get friendly, positive responses.
It works in real-time using OpenAI and can understand mood from the user’s text.

Example:

User: “I’m really stressed about exams.”

KAIRO: “It’s completely normal to feel that way. You’ve prepared well — take it step-by-step, you’ll do great!”

TalkZone helps users improve mental wellness, reduce loneliness, and feel supported every day.



